content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 390.6 - Receipt of provider fee

State Regulations

Payment of the provider fee to a person authorized to sell or market the service contract in this State, or an administrator or other person authorized to receive payment, shall be deemed to be payment to the service contract provider. Notes
